videos.description: Temple guard Shizz Alston knocks down a long 3-pointer coming off the screen.
videos.headline: Alston drains long 3-pointer

videos.description: Temple gets the upset win over undefeated Houston on a last second bucket that was called off due to a charge.
videos.headline: Houston shocked as game tying bucket is called a charge
